title: Back home, Blue Jays break out to beat Royals 11-8 in Game 3 (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,385 Back home, Blue Jays break out to beat Royals 11-8 in Game 3 (Yahoo Sports) Troy Tulowitzki, Josh Donaldson and the slugging Toronto Blue Jays were eager to return to their homer dome after dropping the first two games of the AL Championship Series in Kansas City. The Blue Jays came out swinging and their rowdy fans were singing from the start, with Tulowitzki and Donaldson connecting in a six-run third inning as Toronto roughed up Johnny Cueto and the Royals for an 11-8 victory that cut Kansas City's series lead to 2-1.
